🚀 How to Run
1️⃣ Start the Server
python Ipv6_server.py


Expected output:

[SERVER] IPv6 Server listening on [::1]:1043 ...
[SERVER] Connection from ('::1', <port>, 0, 0)

2️⃣ Start the Client
python IPv6_client.py


Expected output:

[CLIENT] Connected to server [::1]:1043
[CLIENT] Server says: Hello from (Pratham Jariwala) IPv6 server!
[CLIENT] Server replied: Message received. Goodbye! Yamya Sir !!

